Medicaid API Endpoints

Source: R/01-alias_caid.R
medicaid.Rd

Medicaid API Endpoints

Usage

caid_endpoint(alias, call = caller_env())

caid_temporal(alias, call = caller_env())

caid_group(alias, call = caller_env(), ...)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint or group alias

call

<env> environment to use for error reporting

...

Additional arguments passed to the group constructor

Value

An S7 <class_endpoint>, <class_temporal> or <class_group> object

Examples

caid_endpoint("managed_longterm")
